            "verse": 1,
            "text": "Have you seen the one who denies this faith"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 107,
            "verse": 2,
            "text": "For that is the one who drives the orphan away"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 107,
            "verse": 3,
            "text": "and does not encourage the feeding of the poor"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 107,
            "verse": 4,
            "text": "So woe to those who pray"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 107,
            "verse": 5,
            "text": "but, who do not pay attention to their prayer"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 107,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "Those who make a show [of their deeds]"
